{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be dynamic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureNet Cyber Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e50914;\n            --secondary-color: #f2f2f2;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --dark-text-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--brand-color), #b3000a);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            padding: 0.8rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #cccccc;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.7), rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/e50914/ffffff?text=SecureNet+Cyber+Solutions') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .service-card {\n            background: var(--dark-text-color);\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin: 20px 0;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n\n        .service-card h3 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .btn:hover {\n            background: #b3000a;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            background-color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n        }\n\n        #contact {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        input, textarea {\n            width: 80%;\n            max-width: 500px;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin: 10px 0;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n        }\n\n        #contact .btn {\n            width: 80%;\n            max-width: 200px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n\n            nav a {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>SecureNet Cyber Solutions</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#hero\">Home</a>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Your Digital Fortress</h2>\n        <p>Protecting your business in the ever-evolving cyber landscape.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-card\">\n                <h3>Threat Detection & Response</h3>\n                <p>Proactive monitoring and rapid incident handling to minimize impact.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-card\">\n                <h3>Vulnerability Assessment</h3>\n                <p>Identifying weaknesses before attackers do.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-card\">\n                <h3>Security Awareness Training</h3>\n                <p>Empowering your employees to be your first line of defense.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-card\">\n                <h3>Cloud Security Solutions</h3>\n                <p>Securing your cloud infrastructure with advanced measures.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>SecureNet Cyber Solutions is a leading provider of comprehensive cybersecurity services. We are dedicated to safeguarding your digital assets with cutting-edge technology and expert knowledge. Our mission is to provide unparalleled protection and peace of mind to businesses of all sizes.</p>\n            <p>Our team of certified professionals brings years of experience in combating cyber threats, ensuring your business stays secure and compliant.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Ready to enhance your security? Contact us today for a free consultation.</p>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SecureNet Cyber Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch shortly.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}